videoDetails.Title: Graphing the Black YouTube Play Button in Desmos #blackout
videoDetails.Description:
In this video I will speed graph the black YouTube button using desmos the online graphing calculator.  For more desmos tutorials and cool graphs check out my channel.

This graph uses sliders as well as an interesting non-linear curve and restrictions on the x and y values to build the YouTube play button in one equation.

It's a beautiful day to learn!  I want to help you learn math and science that you didn't know before.  If you are looking for more to learn, here are my playlists:
